---
title: "US26 — Share achievements to social media"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>WorkoutSummaryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CreateWorkoutSharePost · ShareWorkoutToSocial
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Post (workout_share)
  A->>B: toggle "Share to Social" on
  B->>C: call(sessionId, caption)
  C->>E: createWorkoutSharePost(sessionId, caption)
  note right of E: public caption only -<br/>private notes are never shared
  E-->>C: postId (Post created)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (shared to community)
  A->>B: pick Facebook / Instagram / Twitter / TikTok
  B->>C: call(platform, text)
  C->>E: shareTo(platform, text)
  E-->>C: ok
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (handed to platform)
  B-->>A: native share opens for chosen platform
  note over E: createWorkoutSharePost via SocialGateway → posts (RLS) - shareTo via SocialShareGateway (Facebook / Instagram / Twitter / TikTok)
